312429505.Title: 19.2 cu. ft. Top Freezer Refrigerator in White
312429505.Description: At GE Appliances, we bring good things to life, by designing and building the world's best appliances. Our goal is to help people improve their lives at home by providing quality appliances that were made for real life. Whether it's enjoying the tradition of making meals from scratch or tackling a mountain of muddy jeans and soccer jerseys, GE Appliances are crafted to support any and every task in the home. Color: White.

205745314.Title: Whirlpool 19.2 cu. ft. Top Freezer Refrigerator in Black
205745314.Description: Complete your kitchen with this Whirlpool 19.2 cu. ft. ENERGY STAR qualified refrigerator. It features adjustable bins not only in the fresh food compartment but also in the freezer which offers the ability to organize and configure for your needs. The humidity controlled crispers allow you to customize how cool you prefer specific fresh food items. This refrigerator also has an optional ice maker kit (model #ECKMFEZ2) which can be purchased separately. Color: Black.

311368579.Title: Frigidaire 18.3 cu. ft. Top Freezer Refrigerator in Black, ENERGY STAR
311368579.Description: The Frigidaire 18.3 cu. ft. Top Freezer features full-width glass shelving in the freezer and refrigerator, a sliding half-width deli drawer, and spacious door bins. Save money and maximize energy efficiency with this ENERGY STAR-certified top-freezer refrigerator. Equipped with bright lighting to keep contents clearly visible. Color: Black.

205758660.Title: Amana 18.2 cu. ft. Top Freezer Refrigerator in Black, Smooth Black
205758660.Description: You will have tons of space to store all of your favorite fresh and frozen foods with this Amana 18 cu. ft. top-freezer refrigerator. The fresh food compartment is quite functional with three shelves, two of them adjustable and one fixed. Also, the six door bins allow you to organize all of those small items that can be easily hidden if placed on the shelves with large items. The icemaker kit which can be purchased separately (model #ECKMF95) will complete the your needs in this refrigerator. Color: Smooth Black.

313892139.Title: LG Electronics 30 in. 20 cu. ft. Top Freezer Refrigerator in White with Mult-Air Flow and Reversible Door
313892139.Description: Capacity means a lot to you, and our top-mount refrigerator features 30 in. width 20 cu. ft. refrigerator and freezer storage space. You're also focused on freshness, and that's why you're sure to appreciate LG's humidity-controlled crisper and full-width gallon door bins. They're on a mission to extend the life of your fruits and vegetables freshness that shines clear through with LG's advanced LED interior lighting. Color: White.

302007875.Title: Frigidaire 20.4 cu. ft. Top Freezer Refrigerator in Stainless Steel, Silver
302007875.Description: The Frigidaire 20.4 cu. ft. Top Freezer Refrigerator features 3 full-width glass shelves and humidity-controlled crisper drawers for storing fruits and vegetables. Equipped with bright lighting to keep contents clearly visible, the refrigerator is easy to control with a single temperature knob inside. On top, the freezer offers a full-width shelf for flexible storage options as well as two full-width door racks to house additional frozen food. Color: Stainless Steel.

302007879.Title: Frigidaire 18 cu. ft. Top Freezer Refrigerator in Black
302007879.Description: The Frigidaire 18.20 cu. ft. Top Freezer has 3 Full-Width Wire Shelves and Crisper Drawers for storing fruits and vegetables. Equipped with bright lighting to keep contents clearly visible. Freezer has a half width shelf for flexible storage options as well as 2 full-width door racks. Color: Black.

205721798.Title: Whirlpool 18.2 cu. ft. Top Freezer Refrigerator in Black
205721798.Description: There's always a place for fresh and frozen favorites inside this Whirlpool 30 in. wide top-freezer refrigerator with 18 cu. ft. capacity. For more convenient storage options above the refrigerator crisper, the Flexi-Slide bin quickly moves side-to-side. Electronic temperature controls let you choose the right temperature for your frozen favorites. Plus, you won't have to fill your ice trays in this top-freezer refrigerator again with the factory-installed icemaker. Color: Black.

300011177.Title: Maytag 18 cu. ft. Top Freezer Refrigerator in Black
300011177.Description: Maytag top-freezer refrigerators are built to hold the cold with features like the Power Cold feature that chills down the refrigerator to help keep everything cool with the touch of a button-even if the whole family's been browsing with the door open. Inside this 18 cu. ft. model you'll also find the BRIGHT SERIES LED lighting. It casts a bright, white light and uses less energy than incandescent bulbs. Color: Black.

310782059.Title: Whirlpool 30 in. 18.25 cu. ft. Top Freezer Refrigerator in Monochromatic Stainless Steel
310782059.Description: There's always a place for fresh and frozen favorites inside the 30 in. wide top-freezer refrigerator with 18 cu. ft. capacity. Frameless glass shelves give your food a little more elbow room for wall-to-wall storage, and electronic temperature controls let you choose the right temperature for your frozen favorites. Plus, you won't have to fill ice trays again inside the top-freezer refrigerator with the easy-to-install EZ Connect icemaker kit. Color: Monochromatic Stainless Steel.

206879439.Title: Amana 18.2 cu. ft. Top Freezer Refrigerator in Black
206879439.Description: This 30 in. wide Amana refrigerator lets you store even more with 18 cu. ft. capacity. The Flip-up Storage, Gallon Door Storage Bins and Humidity-Controlled Crispers give you easy access to all your favorites. Its Glass Shelves are designed to help make cleanup easy so there's no need to cry over spilled milk. Color: Black.

205727475.Title: Whirlpool 19.2 cu. ft. Top Freezer Refrigerator in Black
205727475.Description: Get the flexibility your family needs with purposeful spaces for your family's favorites. The Flexi-Slide™ Bin makes it easier to fit tall items with a bin that quickly and easily moves side to side. Frameless Glass Shelves on select models span from wall to wall so you can store more on each shelf. Then, take advantage of Freezer Temperature Controls so you can keep whatever food you're storing ice cold. Color: Black.

311743494.Title: Frigidaire 18.3 cu. ft. Top Freezer Refrigerator in White
311743494.Description: The Frigidaire 18.3 cu. ft. Top Freezer Refrigerator has 2 full-width glass shelves and two humidity control crisper drawers for storing fruits and vegetables. It's equipped with bright lighting to keep contents clearly visible. The freezer has a full-width glass shelf for flexible storage options as well as 2 full-width door racks. Color: White.

205730499.Title: Whirlpool 18.2 cu. ft. Top Freezer Refrigerator in White
205730499.Description: There's always a place for fresh and frozen favorites inside the Whirlpool 30" wide top-freezer refrigerator with 18 cu. ft. capacity. To give you more convenient storage options above the refrigerator crisper, the Flexi-Slide bin quickly moves side-to-side. Frameless glass shelves give your food a little more elbow room for wall-to-wall storage, and electronic temperature controls let you choose the right temperature for your frozen favorites. Plus, you won't have to fill ice trays again inside the top-freezer refrigerator with the easy-to-install EZ Connect icemaker kit. Color: White.
